data.description: Range price 450k-460k. Gorgeously updated 4 bed 3 bath w/ a den in highly sought after North Ranch Subdivision! Enjoy major upgrades like renewal by Andersen windows, slider doors, a newer roof, OWNED solar, new AC, new water heater, new carpet & custom barn doors throughout. This Immaculately maintained home has been cared for & it shows. From the efficient kitchen, to the office, the artistic mosaic tile creek downstairs, & the double sinks in each bathroom upstairs ''you'll have it all''. The kitchen was designed for entertaining with exposed granite countertops, garnet inlays, a beautiful eat-in island, NEW SS appliances, a prep sink, range w/ in drawer microwave, & cabinets galore that suit every purpose. The primary bedroom has tall vaulted ceilings, walk in closet, & it is ample. That Segways into an en-suite bathroom that is like an oasis to unwind.. Relax in the large private backyard with mature trees, newly installed turf/pavers, block wall, & watch the pretty sunsets. Come see, love it, & stay!
